name: Watercolour Bubble Necklace
description:
Looking for a uniquely hand sculpted necklace in sterling silver and paper. Then this is the modern minimalist piece for you. Light as a feather and soothing watercolours of lilac, mint, pale blue and soft pink mix in this petite style bubble necklace. A perfect piece for any occasion - just right for the office Christmas party and then drinks with the girls! 

This necklace has been completely hand sculpted. It has been sealed with multiple sealants so that you can wear it in the rainiest, hottest, snowiest climates without fear. It wears like any piece of fine jewelry would.

Matching earrings are also available.

Chain: sterling silver with sterling silver lobster clasp
Length: approximately 40cm
Width of Necklace from left to right (top bubble to top bubble): approximately 7cm
Medium: paper, sterling silver, sealants
Colours: lilac, dusty pink, pale green and pale blue

Ships ready packaged in a hard cover leatherette case. Perfect for gift giving.

name: Watercolour bubble earrings
description:
These minimalist contemporary translucent watercolor bubble earrings are comprised of calming hues of jade green, robins egg blue, lilac, and soft pink. These light as a feather earrings are a pretty splash of colour for any day of the year.

Matching necklace also available.

These earrings have been individually hand sculpted. Each earring half is sculpted to match the other half in the pair. Wear them in the rainiest, snowiest, sweatiest climates without fear. They will wear as any piece of fine jewelry would.


Medium: paper, wire, sealed
Colors: jade-ish green, blue, lilac purple, soft pink
Length (with earring hook): approximately 5cms

name: Pale soft pink forget-me-not necklace
description:
Forget Me Not flowers have long been symbolic of love, hope, and memory, making them particularly poignant gifts. This pale pink Forget Me Not pendant sterling silver necklace is a piece of wearable paper art.  

They are perfect gifts for new mothers, best friends, those who have recently lost someone dear to them, or for first anniversary gifts. Hand sculpted to be a minimalist chic piece of jewelry, this pendant will easily transition from work to parties to casual weekends with you!

This necklace has been sealed with multiple sealants so that you can wear it in the rainiest, hottest, snowiest climates without fear. It wears like any piece of fine jewellery should.

The pendant of this necklace hangs from a 44cm delicate sterling silver snake chain. It has a sterling silver lobster clasp. 

Length of pendant: approx 4.5cm
Medium: paper/sterling silver/sealants
Colors: hues of soft pink 

Beautifully presented in a hard cover leatherette case, ready for gift giving!

name: Winter Windswept Tree Necklace
description:
A sterling silver windswept winter tree necklace in a wonderfully delicate design is the perfect bridal piece for a sophisticated bride.  Soft pure white leaves and snowflakes glisten across the branches in an abstract snow design.  

Matching earrings are also available.

This necklace has been sealed with multiple sealants so that you can wear it in the rainiest, sweatiest, snowiest climates without fear. It wears like any piece of fine jewellery should.

The pendant of this necklace hangs from a 44cm delicate sterling silver chain. It has a sterling silver lobster clasp.

Length of pendant: approximately 5 cm
Width of pendant: approximately 5cm
Medium: paper/sterling silver/sealants
Colours: hues of pure snow white 

Beautifully presented in a leatherette case, ready for gift giving.

name: Winter Windswept Tree Earrings
description:
Whispy snow covered branches float delicately from the ear with these unique sterling silver tree earrings. Incredibly light weight, these earrings are a subtle statement piece and add a bit of winter wonder to any outfit. Sculpted to dangle just below the jaw line, they help give the illusion of a long, graceful neckline.

Matching necklace is also available. 

These earrings have been individually handsculpted. Each earring half is sculpted to match the other half in the pair. Wear them in the rainiest, snowiest, hottest climates without fear. They will wear as any piece of fine jewelry would.

These earrings hang from sterling silver earring hooks.

Medium: paper, sterling silver, sealed
Colors: hues of white
Length (with earring hook): approximately 6cms
Width of Earrings at Widest Part: approximately 3cms
